CHANGES
=======

0.6.0
-----

* store history in sqlite instead of yaml
* do not set max_points for graphs
* handle errors in history loading
* save only the end of the history
* save the end of the history, not the beginning

0.5.0
-----

* record history
* switch from openweathermap.org to yweather
* make a new observation in each loop
* always show the graph legend
* update readme for owm

0.4.0
-----

* add OWM weather reporting and labels for traces

0.3.1
-----

* set pid file contents properly
* set minimum versions of dependencies

0.3.0
-----

* add pidfile

0.2.0
-----

* add help to command line args

0.1.0
-----

* ignore build artifacts from pbr
* first working version of daemon
* Initial commit
